{
  "texts": [
    "This initiative demonstrated that adapting curricula to meet the evolving demands of STEM education can significantly impact teacher readiness and effectiveness.",
    "Exemplary Case 6.",
    "Developing Interdisciplinary Competence Models (Song and Guan, 2022, Jinhua, Zhejiang).",
    "Song and Guan (2022) developed a structural model for interdisciplinary competence among STEM teachers, focusing on integrating engineering principles with science education.",
    "The study emphasized the importance of creating supportive environments within schools and fostering collaboration among teachers across different disciplines."
  ]
}